<%
  @title = "Document Contributors"
%>

<h1>Document Contributors</h1>

<p>Once it's up and running, DocumentCloud will be open for anybody gathering original source documents to contribute -- whether professional journalists, bloggers, non-profits. (And of course anybody on the Web will be able to read, search and sort through the documents.) The organizations below have agreed to work with us during our development phase.</p>
		
<p>If you have original documents and you're interested in using DocumentCloud -- it's free -- <a href="mailto:info@documentcloud.org">drop us a line</a>.</p>

<h2>Initial Partners</h2>

<ul>
  <% @partners.each do |name, url| %>
    <li><a href="<%= h(url) %>"><%= h(name) %></a></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<h2>Contributing Organizations</h2>

<ul>
  <% @contributors.each do |name, url, title| %>
    <%= p(name.inspect) %>
    <li><a href="<%= h(url) %>"<%=if title then " title=\"#{h(title)}\"" end %>><%= h(name) %></a></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

